dc_title_s: A map of the provinces of Delhi, Agrah, Oude, and Ellahabad : comprehending the countries lying between Delhi and the Bengal-pro
dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale approximately 1:730,000. Map of the northern provinces of India showing roads, district and provincial boundaries. Relief shown pictorially."Published 12th May, 1794." Dimensions: 107 x 106 centimeters, sheet 56 x 55 centimeters
